import React from 'react' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import "./Campcard.css" function Campcard(prop) { const navigate = useNavigate() function handleclick(){ navigate('/campsq') } return (
Name: {prop.name}
Location: {prop.location}
Num of Refugees: {prop.max_refugees}
Num of Employees : {prop.max_employee}
) } export default Campcard
